      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/ajhale21\">@ajhale21</a> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wave.png?v=12\" title=\":wave:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wave:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Happy 2024! At <a href=\"https://www.upstreamtech.io/monday-com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">upstream</a>, we have an example lessons learned board that is tied into a project management workflow. Looks like this:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/c/dc860802980f66f10f1553d99f8accd67ab4ddf2.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/c/dc860802980f66f10f1553d99f8accd67ab4ddf2_2_690x339.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"339\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1396×687 73.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Is that the sort of thing you’ve got in mind? Happy to provide a demo for you and happy to chat all things <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> any time <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Peta | <a href=\"https://blog.upstreamtech.io/customer-success-stories\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">upstream</a><br />\n<a href=\"mailto:peta@upstreamtech.io\">peta@upstreamtech.io</a><br />\n+613 9067 5611<br />\n<a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/peta8/chat-with-peta\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Or just book straight into my calendar here!</a></p>"
